quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  24,44,aur khuda hi raat aur din ko badalta rehta hai. ahal Basarat ke liye is mein barri Ibrat hai
  24,45,"aur khuda hi ne har chalne phirnay walay jandaar ko pani se pedakiya. to is mein baazay aisay hain ke pait ke bil chaltay hain aur baaz aisay hain jo do paon par chaltay hain aur baaz aisay hain jo chaar paon par chaltay hain. khuda jo chahta hai peda karta hai, be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai"
  24,46,hum hi ne roshan ayatain nazil kee hain aur khuda jis ko chahta hai seedhay raste ki taraf Hadayat karta hai
  24,47,aur baaz log kehte hain ke hum khuda par aur rasool par imaan laaye aur ( un ka ) hukum maan liya phir is ke baad un mein se aik firqa phir jata hai aur yeh log sahib imaan hi nahi hain
  24,48,aur jab un ko khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf bulaya jata hai taakay ( rasool khuda ) un ka qazia chuka den to un mein se aik firqa munh phair laita hai
  24,49,agar ( maamla ) haq ( ho aur ) un ko ( pohanchana ) ho to un ki taraf Mutee ho kar chalay atay hain
  24,50,kiya un ke dilon mein bemari hai ya ( yeh ) shak mein hain ya un ko yeh khauf hai ke khuda aur is ka rasool un ke haq mein zulm karen ge ( nahi ) balkay yeh khud zalim hain
  24,51,mominon ki to yeh baat hai ke jab khuda aur is ke rasool ki taraf bulaye jayen taakay woh un mein faisla karen to kahin ke hum ne ( hukum ) sun liya aur maan liya. aur yahi log Falah panay walay hain
  24,52,aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari kere ga aur is se daray ga to aisay log morad ko pounchanay walay hain
  24,53,"aur ( yeh ) khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke agar tum un ko hukum do to ( sab gharon se ) nikal kharray hon. keh do ke kasmain mat khao, pasandeeda farmabardari ( darkaar hai ). be shak khuda tumahray sab aamaal se khabardaar hai"
